Date created: Jul 27, 2016

Author: Sun-Ting Tsai            lina492375qw1188@gmail.com

There are several ways to generate LAMMPS configuration files. This is
an example of creating a configuration file from LAMMPS output. The
idea is to build a 2D simulation box and to fill the box up with atoms
which organized in the hexagonal structure.

Cite OVITO:
A. Stukowski
Visualization and analysis of atomistic simulation data with OVITO - the Open Visualization Tool 
Modelling Simul. Mater. Sci. Eng. 18 (2010), 015012